Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting like I'm a stranger.\NPlease leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... You have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're tons of people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we carelessly plunge in,\Nwe'll be in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we find out what we're made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have gotten kinda crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and... we'd like you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no longer something as\Nsimple as an assassination, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a group that carries out justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Cipher Pol No. 9,\Nan undercover intelligence agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So thanks to Luffy,\Nthis is our chance to infiltrate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of this is light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuck and can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait... Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Where'd they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One person, and one animal with\Ntwo people. That's all we've confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go guard the bedroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But our foremen are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as too\Nmany guards. Let's go back them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! Third floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the front of the\Npresident's room and the bedroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guards were annihilated!\NSomeone! Come upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tilestone-san!\N--Kaku and Lucci should be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaku! Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, there's no\Nend to this. No word yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a noisy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san had better be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His giant hammer was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N... No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Herculean strength of yours your pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move my arm!\NThere's no way my power can be beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:36.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:39.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:42.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:46.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:05:01.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:08.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:15.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:22.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:26.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:30.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:34.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:37.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:41.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:45.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:48.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:52.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:56.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:59.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:02.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:08.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:11.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:26.94,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"CP9 Takes Off Their Masks!\NTheir Shocking True Faces"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His giant hammer was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N... No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Herculean strength of yours your pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move my arm!\NThere's no way my power can be beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of the foremen have been...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some reinforcements from downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We found them!\N--It's Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They showed up at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that woman this afternoon, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why isn't Luffy here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?! I wanna ask that question!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this, it's like\Nwe've been caught in the act anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go on the offensive,\Nthere's a way to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey, Zoro! What're you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running around the building\Nwon't get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll openly plunge in from\Nthe front and look for Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're shipwrights!\NThey're not our enemy, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll use the back of my swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're inflicting fatal wounds on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I never thought\NI'd see you here... Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We met for the first time last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've wanted to see you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even put your wanted poster up\Nin my room to ensure I never forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you my autograph or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be... nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you wanted to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you go searching for the Poneglyphs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since ancient times,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Government has declared\Nglobally that it's a serious crime
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to seek and decipher the Poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too know of the\Nexistence of the Poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just knowing about it wouldn't be a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only one in the whole world\Nwho can decipher those texts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why the Government\Nput a bounty on your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though you were only eight years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're the only one in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who can restore the ancient weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So you even know about the weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All things considered...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I never thought CP9 was an\Norganization that really existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it does, it means that you've\Nalready left the Straw Hat Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have been helping the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bizarre for a woman who's been\Npursued for 20 years to act like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but, well, that's not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the weapon gets restored through\Ndeciphering the Poneglyphs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether its owner is righteous or evil,\Nthe result will be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weapon can never bring\Nforth "peace" to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world will go under for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't call forth a relic of the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I do agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's none of your business.\NWhatever I do to research history,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you, a stranger, have no\Nright to say anything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... not quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since you and I are in\Nthe same boat, in a sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the blueprints of\Nthe ancient weapon Pluton.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blueprints of the weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pluton is the name of a battleship\Nbuilt on this island a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shipbuilding engineer who created\Nthis overwhelmingly powerful weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had the blueprints passed\Ndown for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He felt that if by some chance\NPluton started running out of control,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there would need to be a force to counter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Government has finally\Nresorted to using force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you're helping\Nthem without knowing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too shocked to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man named Tom,\Nwho entrusted the blueprints with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had been concerned about a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who alone was able to escape from\Nthe Ohara incident 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that although she was small,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was dangerous, since she had the\Nsame ideology as the Ohara devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I inherited the creator's will, so I have\Nthe responsibility of stopping you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Government has come to\Nknow of the existence of the blueprints,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,essentially, it'd be better if I burned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do that, because you're alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so there's still a possibility\Nthat the weapon can be restored!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you want to say before you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect, even if you\Nkilled me and stopped its restoration,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the blueprints get stolen from you,\Nwouldn't it be the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let me tell you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who got taken in by a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was finally able to get out! That was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll swoop in this time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go capture Robin. Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no match for our martial arts skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hand it over already...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or else it'll get dirty with your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought... I could defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Iceberg-san told me to run right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to drop it quickly and run...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's a complete fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but this\Nmeans your plan failed, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic. Sorry, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cocky... You think that you outwitted CP9?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, even though you're only a decoy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't keep you alive now\Nthat you've become involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got stuck! Dammit! I got stuck again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this always happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The rope guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're covered in blood.\NYou sure are full of surprises!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be you! This is the third floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you took the trouble to come\Nto take the crime upon yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Masks! Are they masks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you people must be the ones\Nwho're making Robin do stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Robin back to us, you damn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Hey! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His kicks cut the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got an emergency situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, restrain that guy, too.\NThis is no time for fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. A problem occurred in our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, come to the bedroom right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot Iceberg yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that? Don't shoot Iceberg yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have minded playing\Nwith you a little longer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...something came up. So, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you trying to run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since something came up,\NI gave him a finishing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Lulu-san is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No way...!\N--By just one hit?!\N--Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He flew again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Straw Hat, why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone thinks that you guys are the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... It was all because\Nof our wrong assumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.\NWe're used to being pursued.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, a member of our\Ncrew was taken by masked men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I came to take her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about Nico Robin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong when you fight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, fight with me! I wanna beat them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You do...\N--Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why does Iceberg-san have to be\Nkilled by some totally strange idiots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!\NWho the hell are those people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with the undercover\Nintelligence agency, bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was... my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped me to become\Nan established shipwright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would someone like him be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're too injured to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I want to beat the\Ncrap out of those idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares what happens to my body later on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight to the\Nvery last bone in my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Take these off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Take them off! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing I could give you people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, that puts us in quite a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I tell you first...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when you're about to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You disappointed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've given it to the\NGovernment when they asked nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I wanted to make this town\Npart of my memory without hurting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalifa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you also inherited your\Nmaster's obstinacy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blueno, from the bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys... work for... the Government?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Going undercover\Nwas a pretty easy mission for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, your prudence\Nleaves me at a loss for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Iceberg-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:22:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're the blueprints of\Nthe ancient weapon Pluton?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us, before many people get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:23.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:26.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:32.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:34.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:37.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:46.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:49.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:54.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:00.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:06.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:09.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:19.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me-- you guys are CP9?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tell us where the blueprints are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense. If the ancient weapon is restored,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the world will only fight over its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you don't trust\Nthe power of the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know how humans are, that's all, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Secret Bond! Iceberg and Franky"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
